<title>Overview</title>
<p id="_1efcfa20-efa9-35df-5e45-7980c8a17b53">Conformance with this Standard shall be checked using the tests specified in <xref target="annex_ats">Annex A (normative)</xref> of this document. The framework, concepts, and methodology for testing, and the criteria to claim conformance, are specified in the OGC Compliance Testing Policies and Procedures and the OGC Compliance Testing web site.</p>

<p id="_f7cc94a6-6453-b94d-c4f3-be56375af769">The standardization target of the conformance classes:</p>

