<clause id="_implementations" obligation="normative">
<title>Implementations</title>
<p id="_83b930ca-27a8-85d5-242a-3cdc23ac1c21">Implementors of this Standard select one or more of the <xref target="catalog-requirements-classes">catalog deployment requirements classes</xref> they wish to implement and then implement the required common component requirements classes.</p>
