<td valign="middle" align="left"><p id="_cd16aa0a-be37-344a-0b28-5bf46e2ee108">Each record in a response MAY contain zero or more of the optional properties listed in <xref target="core-properties-record-table"/> and <xref target="core-properties-resource-table"/>.</p>
