<p id="_402e468d-3222-9adc-8066-96f569136430">Many of the properties of the collection, a local resources item, are also properties of a record but the searchability of the collection can be improved by enhancing its information content.  Thus, the following requirements and recommendations are made:</p>

<requirement id="req_local-resources-catalog_mandatory-record-properties" model="ogc"> <identifier>/req/local-resources-catalog/mandatory-record-properties</identifier><component class="part"><p id="_a662b084-4aaa-2464-25af-0b72676b5e23">Each record accessible via the local resource catalog SHALL contain all the mandatory properties listed in <xref target="core-properties-record-table"/> and <xref target="core-properties-resource-table"/>.</p>
</component>
</requirement>

